data.description: Beautiful 2- story home in a highly sought after neighborhood within China Spring ISD. This home features a wonderful open-concept floor plan that includes 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and one-half bathroom.  Downstairs has a separate dining room or could be used as an office. The upstairs has a loft space that could be an additional living area or game room.  Off the loft area is a balcony where you can go out in the evenings to watch the sunset.  It has a nice, oversized pantry and laundry area.  The home has been updated with new floors, new paint, and a remodeled kitchen.  The hall bathroom upstairs has been remodeled and the master bath is in the process of being remodeled and will be done for new owners.  The back yard has a covered patio and above ground pool for enjoying those hot summer days. The central location of this home makes it quick and easy to get anywhere you need to go.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this property yours!
